text: Olof Sundby (6 December 1917, Karlskoga, Sweden - 6 December 1996 in Lund, Sweden) was a Swedish bishop. He was active within the Church of Sweden.. He was the Archbishop of Uppsala between 1972 and 1983. == References == Category:1917 births Category:1996 deaths Category:Swedish clergy Category:Archbishops of Uppsala
